<item>
            <title>[AMQ-6510] Incorrect specification of data dir in conf/log4j.properties </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AMQ-6510</link>
                <project id="12311210" key="AMQ">ActiveMQ Classic</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;conf/log4j.properties specifies the data directory as &lt;/p&gt;
{activemq.base}
&lt;p&gt;/data which doesn&apos;t work if the data directory has been moved elsewhere.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It should be specified as &lt;/p&gt;
{activemq.data}</description>
